# Dockerfile.base
#
# Role
# Skeleton for the shared Docker base image of LAWIM_V2.
#
# Usage futur
# This file will host the common runtime baseline reused by later image-specific
# Dockerfiles.
#
# Conventions
# - keep the base minimal and reproducible;
# - do not add business logic or secrets;
# - keep environment-specific behavior out of this layer.
